{
  "_comment": [
    "All hosting sites (dinify-dev, dinify-stage, dinify-uat) live under the",
    "'dinify-dev' Firebase project. The project name is misleading — it is not",
    "limited to development use. Do NOT rename projects or targets without",
    "updating the deploy-uat.yml workflow and coordinating with the team.",
    "",
    "The 'targets' block maps the deploy target name 'dinify-uat' to the",
    "Firebase hosting site 'dinify-uat'. This target is referenced by the",
    "deploy-uat.yml GitHub Actions workflow. The dinify-dev and dinify-stage",
    "sites in firebase.json do not have explicit target mappings here — they",
    "are deployed directly by site name (e.g. firebase deploy --only hosting:dinify-dev)."
  ],
  "projects": {
    "default": "dinify-dev",
    "uat": "dinify-dev"
  },
  "targets": {
    "dinify-dev": {
      "hosting": {
        "dinify-uat": [
          "dinify-uat"
        ]
      }
    }
  }
}
